[[液化|液化]]或{{le|低溫|cryogenic}}物質的'''膨脹比'''是指在一定量物質在其液體時[[体积|体积]]，和其在[[室溫|室溫]]、一大氣壓力下，氣體時体积的比<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GA_0smWGxwwC&pg=PA22|publisher=CRC Press|date=2007-10-15|isbn=978-0-8493-7969-7|language=en|first=Rick|last=Houghton|title=Emergency Characterization of Unknown Materials|pages=22|access-date=2022-01-27|archive-date=2022-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220127072311/https://books.google.com/books?id=GA_0smWGxwwC&pg=PA22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

若封閉容器中裝有液化物質，而有相當多的液體[[蒸發|蒸發]]，所產生的壓力可能會破壞[[压力容器|压力容器]]。因此需使用{{le|洩壓閥|pressure relief valve}}及{{le|排氣閥|vent valves}}<ref>[http://www.airproducts.com/nr/rdonlyres/38000ecf-e07b-4288-8ff9-73699c70c882/0/safetygram27.pdf Safetygram-27 Cryogenic Liquid Containers] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207051502/http://www.airproducts.com/NR/rdonlyres/38000ECF-E07B-4288-8FF9-73699C70C882/0/safetygram27.pdf|date=2008-12-07}}</ref>。

液化或低溫物質從其沸點到室溫下的膨脹比為：
*[[液氮|液氮]] 1:696
*[[液氦|液氦]] 1:757
*[[氩|氩]] 1:847
*[[液氢|液氢]] 1:851
*[[液氧|液氧]] 1:860
*[[氖|氖]]的膨脹比最高，有1:1445<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5EfhBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA82|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|date=2012-12-06|isbn=978-1-4613-0673-3|language=en|first=Compressed Gas|last=Association|title=Handbook of Compressed Gases|pages=82|access-date=2022-01-27|archive-date=2022-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220127072312/https://books.google.com/books?id=5EfhBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA82|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Characteristics|url=http://www.lindecanada.com/en/aboutboc/safety/cryogenic_liquids/characteristics.php|publisher=The Linde Group|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218125124/http://www.lindecanada.com/en/aboutboc/safety/cryogenic_liquids/characteristics.php|archive-date=2012-02-18}}</ref>。

